Jonathan Cake https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Cake 0 Jonathan James Cake (born 31 August 1967) is an English actor who has worked on various TV programmes and films. His notable screen roles include Jack Favell in Rebecca (1997), Oswald Mosley in Mosley (1997), Japheth in the NBC television film Noah's Ark (1999), Tyrannus in the ABC miniseries Empire (2005) and Det. Chuck Vance on the ABC drama series Desperate Housewives (2011–2012). Jonathan_James_Cake ( born 31_August_1967 ) is an_English_actor who has_worked on various_TV_programmes_and_films .
